<B>__{kobo}
<A>__{waits and waits. nick draws closer. then, kobo tears off back down the mountain, shooting past nick. nick brakes... he slows down, and starts to turn, but the wheels whirl on the gravel and the bike goes into a skid, heading right for the edge of the road.}
